ActProtecting Canada's Immigration System Act
SubjectOrder Fixing December 15, 2012 as the Day on which Certain Sections of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing December 15, 2012 as the day on which sections 7 and 8, subsection 9(1), sections 17 to 22, subsection 23(1), sections 29 and 33 to 35, subsections 38(1) and (2) and section 39, 41 to 46, 49 to 51 and 53 of the PROTECTING CANADA'S IMMIGRATION SYSTEM ACT, chapter 17 of the Statutes of Canada, 2012, COME INTO FORCE.
